# рҹҡҖ Terraform AWS Infrastructure

## рҹ“Ң Overview
Provision AWS infrastructure using Terraform including VPC, EC2, and S3.

## рҹӣ пёҸ Tech Stack
- Terraform (IaC)
- AWS (Cloud)

## вҡҷпёҸ Features
- Modular Terraform code
- Remote backend (S3 + DynamoDB)
- Scalable infrastructure design

## рҹҡҖ Usage
```bash
terraform init
terraform apply